## Requirements

- Svelte 5.0+
- Tailwind CSS 4.0+
- Node.js 18+ or Bun

## Installation

Install via git dependency:

```bash
bun add github:kiwiworks/ukiyoe
```

## Peer Dependencies

Ukiyoe requires these peer dependencies:

```bash
bun add bits-ui @lucide/svelte @internationalized/date tailwindcss
```

## Tailwind Configuration

Import the Ukiyoe preset in your Tailwind config:

```typescript
// tailwind.config.ts
import ukiyoePreset from 'ukiyoe/tailwind.preset';

export default {
  presets: [ukiyoePreset],
  content: [
    './src/**/*.{html,js,svelte,ts}',
    './node_modules/ukiyoe/dist/**/*.{html,js,svelte,ts}'
  ]
};
```

## Import Styles

Import the base styles in your app entry:

```typescript
import 'ukiyoe/styles.css';
```

## Usage

Import and use components:

```svelte
<script>
  import { Button, Input, Badge } from 'ukiyoe';
</script>

<Button variant="primary">Click me</Button>
<Input placeholder="Enter text..." />
<Badge variant="success" text="Active" />
```

